This is a collection of functions for working with Stanley simplicial poset rings.

To install this package, exectute "M2 install.m2" in the project directory.

After you have it installed, you can include this package by running

loadPackage("SimplicialPosets").

To view the documentation, navigate to the following directory:

~/.Macaulay2/local/share/doc/Macaulay2/SimplicialPosets/html/

Then, open "toc.html" in your web browser.